  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Requires sentencing court to consider whether defendant is parent of child, or caregiver of elderly, disabled or terminally ill person whose well-being would be adversely affected by the person's incarceration and if so, shall impose a non-jail sentence."
    }
